How to use this Licence

To use this Licence, in compliance with Article 5.3, the Licensee has to include the
Notice in the distributed copies. The Notice has to be included in a copy of the
Licence in all the official languages of the European Union.

However, the Notice can be included in a translated version in any language as far as
the translation is accurate and complete and clearly indicates that it is a
non-official translation.

The name of the European Union institution which developed the Work and its
contributors, when mentioned in the Work, shall not be used for advertising or
otherwise to imply endorsement of commercial products or services, in particular
by using the name of the Work or its contributors as trademarks.


